Place 1 cookie, top down, into a small clear dessert bowl (such as a custard cup or martini glass). Place 1 truffle in center. Top with second cookie, top up; pressing to from cookie around truffle, allowing cookie to break across top slightly exposing truffle, and pressing sides together to seal. Repeat with remaining cookies and truffles. Place in refrigerator until ready to serve. To serve, microwave (HIGH) 20-30 seconds. Top with a scoop of ice cream, if desired.